---
title; asciibin - ASCII to Binary to ASCII Converter
---
<p>Behold the raw power of ASCII to binary conversion done via a small JavaScript function.  Enter text in the left box and convert it into binary to tabbing out of the box or clicking the &#8216;update&#8217; button.  You can also convert binary into text if you&#8217;re so inclined.</p>
